channel.title: [508] Ultimate Boredom [508]
channel.description:
THIS IS NOT MY WORK, I AM POSTING FOR ZACK_FLOWERS SINCE HE'S BANNED.
This is a base from pali, but changed imports to Bulby.
(REMEMBER THIS IS AN UNFINISHED BASE, FEEL FREE TO LEECH OR DO WHAT U WANT WITH IT!)
Currently there are 13 working noncombat skills. They include:
Mining Smithing Fishing Cooking Firemaking Woodcutting Summoning (Npc's don't follow you) Agility (a crappy base but it works) Herblore Thieving (Only Stalls added, adding pickpocketing later) Crafting (Only chisel+gems atm, adding leather crafting soon) Fletching Hunting Runecrafting Construction (Used "My Construction" tutorial to add this base, haven't edited anything yet) Slayer- Haven't added npc's yet. Farming - Figuring out the Bulby farming and going to create my own. Combat skills--Haven't added npc's yet, but you can add npc aggression easily.
[System Updates] -Working bank/bank notes, haven't tried adding withdraw/deposit x yet. -Almost perfect trade, just have to add offer/remove x -shops with Buy 50/buy 10 -Working private chat -Almost like z508 pvp, but not quite sure. -Working IPBan
